      <title><![CDATA[生成指定时间内的时间列表]]></title>
      <url>https://pemako.github.com/2017/01/21/python-gen-datalist/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="获取从指定开始时间到指定结束时间的列表"><a href="#获取从指定开始时间到指定结束时间的列表" class="headerlink" title="获取从指定开始时间到指定结束时间的列表"></a>获取从指定开始时间到指定结束时间的列表</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> datetime</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">date_range1</span><span class="params">(start, end)</span>:</span></div><div class="line">    days = (datetime.datetime.strptime(end, <span class="string">"%Y%m%d"</span>) - datetime.datetime.strptime(start, <span class="string">"%Y%m%d"</span>)).days + <span class="number">1</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> [datetime.datetime.strftime(datetime.datetime.strptime(start, <span class="string">"%Y%m%d"</span>) + datetime.timedelta(i), <span class="string">"%Y%m%d"</span>) <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> xrange(days)]</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">date_range2</span><span class="params">(beginDate, endDate)</span>:</span></div><div class="line">    dates = []</div><div class="line">    dt = datetime.datetime.strptime(beginDate, <span class="string">"%Y%m%d"</span>)</div><div class="line">    date = beginDate[:]</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> date &lt;= endDate:</div><div class="line">        dates.append(date)</div><div class="line">        dt = dt + datetime.timedelta(<span class="number">1</span>)</div><div class="line">        date = dt.strftime(<span class="string">"%Y%m%d"</span>)</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> dates</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">dt_list = date_range1(<span class="string">'20161218'</span>, <span class="string">'20161220'</span>)</div><div class="line">// [<span class="string">'20161218'</span>, <span class="string">'20161219'</span>, <span class="string">'20161220'</span>]</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
    </entry>
    
